      • getRecoveryRate

        public float getRecoveryRate()
        Returns the recovery rate of the Hero (depends on its type). The recovery rate is a multiplier used when calculating the amount of time to heal. A value of < 1 means that the hero will heal slower. A value of > 1 means that the hero will heal faster.
        Returns:
        RecoveryRate of the Hero
